+	  - CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET:
+	  - CONFIG_ENV_SIZE:
+
+	  These two #defines specify the offset and size of the environment
+	  area within the first NAND device.  CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET must be
+	  aligned to an erase block boundary.
+
